Any Android-specific modifications follow the **Apache License 2.0**, ensuring compatibility with the Android Open Source Project (AOSP). However, modifications must remain open-source.

#### c) Root-Level Modifications
For root-based system enhancements, the license remains **GPL v3** to protect user freedoms while modifying core system components.

